source.title: Ukraine: Zelenskyy in UK for talks with allies on missiles - DW
source.name: DW (English)

facts: Meeting of Ukraine's key European allies, 'coalition of the willing', taking place
The trip follows EU leaders vowing to keep funding Kyiv's defense

neutral.headline: Ukrainian President Zelenskyy in UK for meeting with European allies on missile support.
neutral.body_html: President of Ukraine, Volodymyr Zelenskyy is currently visiting the United Kingdom to meet with key members of Europe's 'coalition of willing'. This comes after EU leaders have pledged continued financial backing for Kyiv’s defense efforts.

conservative.headline: Zelenskyy in UK: Strengthening Ukraine with European Allies' Support on Missiles.
conservative.body_html: Ukrainian President Zelenskyy is meeting with key members of Europe’s ‘coalition of willing’ to discuss missile support for Kyiv. This comes after EU leaders have pledged continued financial backing.
